<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.1.8">
<l>māli ṉantuḻāy varumeṉ ṉeñcakam</l>
<l>māli ṉantuḻāy vanteṉ ṉuḷpuka</l>
<l>kōla vāṭaiyum koṇṭu vantatōr</l>
<l>āli vantatā laritu kāvalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My inner heart comes searching for Māl’s company.</l>
<l>That which the beautiful north wind brought, coming with Māl’s lovely tulasī</l>
<l>To pierce my core, came in [just] one raindrop!</l>
<l>Protection [from it] is daunting!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
